{"tid":268473,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【那些年系列】唔係講笑，R4簡直係NDS既聖物","createTime":"2017-06-03T05:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T19:05:34.000Z","uid":34884,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b558c901117b7971fc0649497ede2d6c333bbe8b","tid":268473,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:35:04.000Z","msg":"幾歲嗰陣玩Gameboy Color，唔知邊個天才整左啲咩32合1既遊戲帶，插一餅帶就可以玩晒咁多隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢啲帶通常都冇得save，每次開都要重玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小學嗰陣有部GBA SP，會買老翻帶玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣唔識分喺遊戲機鋪買嗰啲8x蚊既帶係正版定翻版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剩係知清一色有個勁似正版帶既盒，入面有張印到好濛既說明書同餅深灰色既GBA帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（後來我先知正版帶好多唔同既顏色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n差唔多小學畢業既時候聽同學講有張叫Supercard既卡，可以將啲game dl然後入落張SD再插落去GBA玩<br />\n<br />\n不過已經太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲人開始玩NDS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nNDS磚機嗰陣都唔算太多人玩，係去到我中二嗰陣出NDSL先多人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能係NDSL啲色靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣見到好多女仔都有玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而嗰陣有留意開都知嗰陣有張燒錄卡叫R4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用張1GB MicroSD卡入晒十幾廿隻中意既Game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣NDS啲game都係32MB起跳，大型少少都要64MB，去到PKM黑白直情要128MB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就用嚟入Pkm，應援團，mario Kart同星之卡比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣老任都開始醒，每出一隻大作都加密，結果要等R4個網出patch先可以玩<br />\n<br />\nR4仲有個好正既功能，就係可以聽歌睇戲睇小說！<br />\n以前啲手機冇依家咁勁，有支援SD/M2卡，3.5mm耳機頭同播mp3檔是但一樣已經好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我就將啲歌入落去張R4卡到帶出街聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nR4嗰排直頭紅到日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而R4亦好似依家既芭蕉扇咁，出左好多一模一樣樣但唔係官網出品既燒錄卡（即係老翻既老翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n乜撚野R4 II，R4金版銀版&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最撚慘係買左呢啲老翻唔知邊日會冇更新冇得再玩新game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住同福仁二樓堆老翻檔一樣唔知幾時開始無人問津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不知不覺就去到3DS既世代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留得底既好多都係hardcore，而且會買正版<br />\n<br />\n不過點都好，依家問返你對NDS既印象真係不得不提R4卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a45718c651cea6c4edc47b4d30a7e98c482a8e","tid":268473,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"買帶，未用過 R4"},{"pid":"68ac980c3c61a7d54edce72d57a7d0e3aa6c777b","tid":268473,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:39:35.000Z","msg":"未用過R4<br />\n到後期都有模擬器連部機都唔駛"},{"pid":"f2c42a5ce3ab6bd80c97e41b4894917fdc6344dc","tid":268473,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:43:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買帶，未用過 R4</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd70c0878830d005b6b13625dd360fdb1efd47d7","tid":268473,"uid":34884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未用過R4<br />\n到後期都有模擬器連部機都唔駛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但始終冇嗰種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7c0021a304f796f10205b0e8d5d78da4c431ee","tid":268473,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc