 />\n以前既事嚟架喇師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前讀中小學，唔係個個都有Daddy Mammy畀零用錢去買呢樣買嗰樣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正版帶我記得好似幾百蚊一隻game, 冇R4 ndsl唔會普及得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家3DS冇人再買呢啲卡架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部從晒良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4955b296ffd9384150f2daf5a5c58090b4f4d5a5","tid":268473,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"R4代言人.jpg"},{"pid":"ed3dcc05114e1c91e83ab5c93e4dfccf04f3511a","tid":268473,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T07:24:30.000Z","msg":"好有回憶，窮人恩物"},{"pid":"96f187957d36c5495fa65d9782361e5f7ae5eb81","tid":268473,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T07:48:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好有回憶，窮人恩物</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef961d7dca026ca2823e63e465c369bfa716ade","tid":268473,"uid":43856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T07:52:37.000Z","msg":"邊度有仲有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97977b966117dace7e8c8542eb2c6f438a1c88a7","tid":268473,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊度有仲有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買New 3DS啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋有能力就從良啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4918a5b8ef1890327b1e9cd98ad1cf6f1a55784","tid":268473,"uid":37933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T08:56:27.000Z","msg":"當年好多日文game唔漢化真係唔識玩<br />\neg逆轉系列 雷頓教授<br />\n依家人大左 買game玩game都會用正版<br />\n但係如果要玩逆轉或者其他文本多劇情重嘅game<br />\n冇漢化真係無咩癮玩落去<br />\n利申: ipad買左新果隻逆轉5定6嘅英文版 玩左陣頂唔順英文配音同堆譯名 封左麈"},{"pid":"02ea63f3b49ed917c05ee4384315e3dfc9f1b990","tid":268473,"uid":4081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"當年唔用R4都唔知要帶幾多帶出街"},{"pid":"575a4ae77558db4e1fe2e511ea93df372127e450","tid":268473,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年好多日文game唔漢化真係唔識玩<br />\neg逆轉系列 雷頓教授<br />\n依家人大左 買game玩game都會用正版<br />\n但係如果要玩逆轉或者其他文本多劇情重嘅game<br />\n冇漢化真係無咩癮玩落去<br />\n利申: ipad買左新果隻逆轉5定6嘅英文版 玩左陣頂唔順英文配音同堆譯名 封左麈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917470c14c7053d815d1ec173806a7f70396839f","tid":268473,"uid":73991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>R4代言人.jpg</blockquote><br />\nStephy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5a628092b6387a6375ef7ac0a91ea1d79054f6","tid":268473,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:55:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f6fd2643af622dd72faa9a8cbe5c17894f40627","tid":268473,"uid":68236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:56:51.000Z","msg":"童年回憶<br />\n當年好窮，屋企無電腦但唔知點解有部NDSL<br />\n用R4但自己入唔到game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果要去電腦/game舖佢10蚊一隻同我入<br />\n果陣好鍾意玩lost in blue同太鼓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df68e0f859bd60bd44ac06bbd7a6a4d8820ad957","tid":268473,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>R4代言人.jpg</blockquote><br />\nStephy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nR4一開始得白色真係敗筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/w5659ml205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fw5659ml205.jpg&h=057e8227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/t42511劉pzp205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Ft42511%E5%8A%89pzp205.jpg&h=cfcf0fb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/a52132Assyolin2t205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fa52132Assyolin2t205.jpg&h=5c739adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/w1004Jessica-s-R4q205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fw1004Jessica-s-R4q205.jpg&h=150b86b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/v219StephyR4k205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fv219StephyR4k205.jpg&h=0cb2fa27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30fd5556dcd8329c866c269d14e3c3179765963f","tid":268473,"uid":76563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"BINC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d52308f59855ecdbbf88edb37ed662699dabba5","tid":268473,"uid":34884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>童年回憶<br />\n當年好窮，屋企無電腦但唔知點解有部NDSL<br />\n用R4但自己入唔到game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果要去電腦/game舖佢10蚊一隻同我入<br />\n果陣好鍾意玩lost in blue同太鼓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLost in blue都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n孤島去搜集資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cf735564583634c3f49f3f9091f8e077b49762","tid":268473,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾歲嗰陣玩Gameboy Color，唔知邊個天才整左啲咩32合1既遊戲帶，插一餅帶就可以玩晒咁多隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢啲帶通常都冇得save，每次開都要重玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小學嗰陣有部GBA SP，會買老翻帶玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣唔識分喺遊戲機鋪買嗰啲8x蚊既帶係正版定翻版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剩係知清一色有個勁似正版帶既盒，入面有張印到好濛既說明書同餅深灰色既GBA帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（後來我先知正版帶好多唔同既顏色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n差唔多小學畢業既時候聽同學講有張叫Supercard既卡，可以將啲game dl然後入落張SD再插落去GBA玩<br />\n<br />\n不過已經太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲人開始玩NDS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nNDS磚機嗰陣都唔算太多人玩，係去到我中二嗰陣出NDSL先多人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能係NDSL啲色靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣見到好多女仔都有玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而嗰陣有留意開都知嗰陣有張燒錄卡叫R4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用張1GB MicroSD卡入晒十幾廿隻中意既Game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣NDS啲game都係32MB起跳，大型少少都要64MB，去到PKM黑白直情要128MB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就用嚟入Pkm，應援團，mario Kart同星之卡比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣老任都開始醒，每出一隻大作都加密，結果要等R4個網出patch先可以玩<br />\n<br />\nR4仲有個好正既功能，就係可以聽歌睇戲睇小說！<br />\n以前啲手機冇依家咁勁，有支援SD/M2卡，3.5mm耳機頭同播mp3檔是但一樣已經好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我就將啲歌入落去張R4卡到帶出街聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nR4嗰排直頭紅到日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而R4亦好似依家既芭蕉扇咁，出左好多一模一樣樣但唔係官網出品既燒錄卡（即係老翻既老翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n乜撚野R4 II，R4金版銀版&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最撚慘係買左呢啲老翻唔知邊日會冇更新冇得再玩新game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住同福仁二樓堆老翻檔一樣唔知幾時開始無人問津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不知不覺就去到3DS既世代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留得底既好多都係hardcore，而且會買正版<br />\n<br />\n不過點都好，依家問返你對NDS既印象真係不得不提R4卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3ds 有冇得用類近r4 ge 野<br />\n聽人講會鎖機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求救 我想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家真係唔建議你買呢啲卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨時得不償失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ddca52b68a4849f4294b5adfde9935079188be","tid":268473,"uid":4301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:25:34.000Z","msg":"以前唔知fox會奶嘢 成日down  .nds 遊戲 玩幾日張sd卡就會中毒"},{"pid":"969dab20b7bc550a8eb38d68f54156ef23d36c68","tid":268473,"uid":4330,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:29:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩老番仲咁撚理直氣壯既咩而家D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正義撚縮番入你老母個西度啦"},{"pid":"63a0568a77b917d67be5b3b54963b8ab23243bc1","tid":268473,"uid":72203,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>玩老番仲咁撚理直氣壯既咩而家D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正義撚縮番入你老母個西度啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩老番仲可以屌番人轉頭,勁"},{"pid":"4d18e9b0c01a4f4aa2290e885c982577f33937f6","tid":268473,"uid":76563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:41:55.000Z","msg":"以前初初打機乜都唔識<br />\n叫同學幫手買機 就係用R4<br />\n嗰時覺得好方便 上網就可以下載GAME<br />\nlost in blue、應援團、mario kart<br />\n玩極都唔厭<br />\n<br />\n宜家有能力買game<br />\n反而無心機玩 玩兩玩就封塵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cade27919549bcca07e96423e6c7fb88c926ef","tid":268473,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:45:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>玩老番仲咁撚理直氣壯既咩而家D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正義撚縮番入你老母個西度啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩老番仲可以屌番人轉頭,勁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打我冇話你講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我地應該用正版既<br />\n<br />\n只係嗰陣初中又唔夠秤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返唔到pt<br />\n屋企又畀得好少零用錢，只係夠搭車食飯<br />\n新年利是錢得1200，真係死慳死抵先啱啱好買到部NDSL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀大學開始有補習同返pt intern有閒錢就買返晒正版喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就連當年玩R4冇錢買既Pkm都買返晒返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5pcb3was\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5pcb3was&h=fec6a9ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/h5x23l4d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh5x23l4d&h=1ae007c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89ac2d03ee3f4725fbdcbb054d713e5b7f677935","tid":268473,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor