:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1087347015c01e2a7102bfb0603581ca4b487ccd","tid":268473,"uid":72203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>玩老番仲咁撚理直氣壯既咩而家D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正義撚縮番入你老母個西度啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩老番仲可以屌番人轉頭,勁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打我冇話你講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我地應該用正版既<br />\n<br />\n只係嗰陣初中又唔夠秤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返唔到pt<br />\n屋企又畀得好少零用錢，只係夠搭車食飯<br />\n新年利是錢得1200，真係死慳死抵先啱啱好買到部NDSL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀大學開始有補習同返pt intern有閒錢就買返晒正版喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就連當年玩R4冇錢買既Pkm都買返晒返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5pcb3was\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5pcb3was&h=fec6a9ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/h5x23l4d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh5x23l4d&h=1ae007c6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都明,但而家有D人玩老番仲理直氣壯屌番D正版既人正義撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2abc060e1011f67bbf065a46bfb2f74580457e","tid":268473,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:10:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef59f4292d08df06a890eb3316c04f01bdc56f03","tid":268473,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:20:21.000Z","msg":"用黎玩應援團<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後期用黎睇動話，之前仲未有好多smartphone<br />\n<br />\n有得聽歌睇劇好正"},{"pid":"3eb073751c6e05879d3d22ec176301b56ec50b6b","tid":268473,"uid":82279,"li